data.title: Underwater Hockey
data.meta_description: Recently, I received assignment to cover a pick up game of underwater hockey; in my mind, I was thinking Underwater Hockey, What the Puck!? I never heard of underwater hockey until that point. I must say, this was an awesome assignment.
